Example of species ranges as SpatialPolygonsDataFrame

Source: R/data_documentation.R
species_data.Rd

An object of class SpatialPolygonsDataFrame.

species_data

Format

data.frame:

data

data.frame with 25 rows and 1 column

polygons

SpatialPolygons

proj4string

object of class CRS

Examples

data("species_data", package = "biosurvey")

species_data

#> class       : SpatialPolygonsDataFrame 
#> features    : 25 
#> extent      : -115.6194, -87.5921, 15.2692, 31.88795  (xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax)
